{
  "stem": "12053.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of children lost their possessions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a very treasured possession, gold watch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had a little ring bought in the same shops.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were customers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think my parents made a contract with them for the laundry that they used to give us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had a little tiny ring with a tiny little diamond in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when I came to England, they told me I couldn't wear it on my left finger.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because that's-- it shouldn't be taken full of engagement ring.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was quite a sophisticated nearly 16-year-old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they told me to put it on the other-- I lost it in the blitz when we were bombed out in country.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But little things like that I took with me and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] writing paper and things like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But actually, we, we had quite a peaceful journey, not like some of my friends that I hear about.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was hard, but not unduly so, because we thought it was an adventure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- they, they, they didn't show how sad they were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my sister, later on, she always said the most important thing for her was my mother shouldn't cry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because she remembers a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She also came to see us off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At first they-- in those days, they were still allowed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was one of the first transports out from Munich on the 6th of-- we left on the fourth of January, 1939.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was only a few weeks after the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my experiences of the Hitler times, the worst of the Hitler times, are not as steep as my sister's, who experienced a lot more, though she is much younger.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
